<section>
<title>Detailed Description</title>

<para>HTTP API service implementation using HttpClient. </para>



<para>This service provides HTTP request capabilities with support for: </para>

<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem>

<para>All HTTP verbs </para>
</listitem>
<listitem>

<para>Multiple authentication modes </para>
</listitem>
<listitem>

<para>Automatic retry with exponential backoff </para>
</listitem>
<listitem>

<para>Request/response logging and telemetry </para>
</listitem>
</itemizedlist>
</para>

